	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Exotic Goods</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP">
			<Text>Your Foreign Advisor writes that the caravan has stopped off in a City State. She has set about securing a set possible trade deals. However, the Merchants are in vicious competition, and signing a deal with one will alienate you from the rest.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Trade 3 [ICON_RES_HORSE] Horses for a copy of [ICON_RES_IVORY] Ivory.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Pay {1_YieldCost} to learn the {2_InstantYield} required to produce one copy of [ICON_RES_GLASS] Glass.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Pay {1_YieldCost} to establish a distinct style of pottery, worth {2_InstantYield} and a copy of [ICON_RES_PORCELAIN] Porcelain.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Pay {1_YieldCost} to impress foreign dignitaries with a copy of fine [ICON_RES_JEWELRY] Jewelry, gaining {2_InstantYield}.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>I am willing to hand over several thoroughbreds in exchange for a supply of these 'elephants'.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>This fine glassware intrigues me. We lack the scientific ability to produce something so fragile.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>And to think we had been eating out of Iron bowls this whole time. Who knew this Porcelain material existed?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>If these jewelers can do what they boast of, every foreign dignitary in the Capital will be green with envy.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
